---
import "../styles/global.css";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import headerImage from "../assets/header.jpg";
import lowerWaves from "../assets/logo/logoCMPlowerWavesColored.svg";
---

<section 
  class="relative w-full h-[80vh] min-h-[650px] flex items-center bg-white"
>
  <!-- Overlay -->
  <div class="
    absolute inset-0 z-10 
    bg-gradient-to-t from-[rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] to-[rgba(0,0,0,0)]
  ">
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="w-full w-full mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:flex-row items-center md:items-start">
    <div 
      class="
        relative z-20 px-6 
        w-full lg:w-4/4 xl:w-2/3 
        mt-40
        text-white 
      "
    >
      <div class="w-full text-center space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-full px-6 py-2.5 text-white">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#37A4B3]" fill="white" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M9 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM17 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM12.93 17c.046-.327.07-.66.07-1a6.97 6.97 0 00-1.5-4.33A5 5 0 0119 16v1h-6.07zM6 11a5 5 0 015 5v1H1v-1a5 5 0 015-5z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="font-medium">Centre de pneumologie à Lyon</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl text-white font-header md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
          La santé de vos
          <span class="text-transparent [-webkit-text-stroke:2px_white]">
            poumons <br />
          </span>
          entre de bonnes mains
        </h1>

        <p class="text-base md:text-xl opacity-90">
          Parce que bien respirer est essentiel à votre qualité de vie, notre centre de pneumologie vous propose un accompagnement personnalisé et attentif. Nos médecins prennent le temps de comprendre vos besoins pour vous offrir un suivi médical clair, rassurant et adapté à votre situation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Logo ovale -->
  <div 
    class="
      absolute  
      bg-white p-4 rounded-full
      z-30 flex items-center justify-center
      left-1/2 bottom-0 transform 
      -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2
    "
  >
    <Image 
      src={lowerWaves}
      alt="Logo waves" 
      class="h-6 md:h-8 w-auto"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Background image -->
  <Image 
    src={headerImage}
    alt="Hero Image" 
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center z-0"
  />
</section>